==English==
===Noun===
'''[[shit]]-[[eating]] [[grin]]'''
#{{idiom}} {{colloquial}} {{vulgar}} 1) A [[smug]], self-confident expression indicating a ridiculously [[arrogant]] sureness. 2) a look of extreme satisfaction on someone's face that is annoying to other people who are less happy.

===Quotations===
*"What I'm doing right now&mdash;lounging around, wearing a shit-eating grin&mdash;is the most irresponsible, despicable, reprehensible thing I could possibly do." [http://www.montrealmirror.com/ARCHIVES/2001/042601/news7.html]
*"Best of all, the novel's American president, a braying megalomaniac, is clearly inspired by the photo on Kelly's studio wall: The president's shit-eating grin when he sees his first giant robot warrior is itself worth the price of admission." [http://www.citypages.com/databank/25/1208/article11841.asp]